===Phrasebook===
'''[[I]] [[hate]] [[you]]'''

# {{pejorative}} Pejorative expression of [[hatred]], or intense [[disdain]] or [[dislike]] directed at someone.
#: ''He told his mother, "'''I hate you''' for giving him $10 when he didn't work for it and I had to!"''
# An affirmation of dislike directed at someone.

